data.description: Conveniently located, this home is the epitome of comfort and functionality. Boasting an open concept design, it exudes warmth and charm, having been meticulously maintained. Situated on a generous lot, ample parking and a sprawling fenced backyard make it ideal for hosting gatherings with friends and loved ones. Step inside to discover a move-in ready sanctuary, featuring solid surface floors throughout for easy maintenance. For culinary enthusiasts, the kitchen is a dream come true, equipped with granite countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a spacious island, and abundant cabinet space. The convenience of a laundry room adjacent to the kitchen enhances the practicality of daily routines. Additionally, a bonus space/storage area off the formal dining room provides flexibility and extra utility. Whether you're relaxing indoors or entertaining outdoors, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style.
